data.description: ***HUGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT*** Gorgeous South Jordan home on a large .39 acre lot.  This beauty has been well kept and boasts an open layout with stunning custom kitchen, complete with double ovens, gas range and stainless steel appliances.   Enjoy the formal dining room with extra custom cabinetry space, plenty of natural light and plantation shutters throughout. Large master bedoom complete with additional ceiling height, large tub and walk in closet.  This .39 acre back yard is perfect for summer barbecues and comes complete with a HUGE RV parking space, just right for all of your toys or for a shop.  You will LOVE this home.
